	<a name="footnote33-02211_000_030">33.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/41.3?lang=eng#2" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Alma 41:3</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/137.9?lang=eng#8" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 137:9</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-02211_000_030"><a name="-02211_000_030">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote34-02211_000_030">34.</a>
      </span>
				<p>&ldquo;Messages of Inspiration from President Monson,&rdquo; <span class="emphasis">Church News,</span> July 5, 2008, 2.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-02211_000_030"><a name="-02211_000_030">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote35-02211_000_030">35.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.27?lang=eng#26" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">2&nbsp;Nephi 2:27</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.8?lang=eng#7" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Jacob 6:8</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-02211_000_030"><a name="-02211_000_030">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote36-02211_000_030">36.</a>
      </span>
				<p>Satan wants us to be miserable, as he is (see <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/rev/12.9?lang=eng#8" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Revelation 12:9</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.18?lang=eng#17" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">2&nbsp;Nephi 2:18</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.22-27?lang=eng#21" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 10:22&ndash;27</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/moses/4.6?lang=eng#5" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moses 4:6</a>).</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-02211_000_030"><a name="-02211_000_030">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote37-02211_000_030">37.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.12-14?lang=eng#11" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Alma 5:12&ndash;14</a>. Such a mighty change includes repentance, forgiveness, and a renewed determination to &ldquo;come unto Christ, and be perfected in him&rdquo; (<a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.32?lang=eng#31" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moroni 10:32</a>).</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-02211_000_030"><a name="-02211_000_030">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote38-02211_000_030">38.</a>
      </span>
				<p>&ldquo;The first principles and ordinances of the Gospel are: first, Faith in the Lord Jesus Christ; second, Repentance; third, Baptism by immersion for the remission of sins; fourth, Laying on of hands for the gift of the Holy Ghost&rdquo; (<a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/pgp/a-of-f/1.4?lang=eng#3" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Articles of Faith 1:4</a>). Repentance requires a complete change for the better&mdash;a total personal upgrade.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-02211_000_030"><a name="-02211_000_030">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote39-02211_000_030">39.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.1?lang=eng#0" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 93:1</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-02211_000_030"><a name="-02211_000_030">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote40-02211_000_030">40.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.32?lang=eng#31" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Moroni 10:32</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-02211_000_030"><a name="-02211_000_030">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote41-02211_000_030">41.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.13-14?lang=eng#12" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 93:13&ndash;14</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-02211_000_030"><a name="-02211_000_030">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote42-02211_000_030">42.</a>
      </span>
				<p><a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.19?lang=eng#18" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 93:19</a>; see also <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/66.2?lang=eng#1" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">D&amp;C 66:2</a>; <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.5-6?lang=eng#4" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">132:5&ndash;6</a>.</p>
			</li>
			<li class="footnote " id="-02211_000_030"><a name="-02211_000_030">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">
	<a name="footnote43-02211_000_030">43.</a>
      </span>
				<p>See Bruce&nbsp;R. McConkie, <span class="emphasis">Mormon Doctrine,</span> 2nd ed. (1966), 118.</p>
			</li>
		</ol>
                                        
